<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2><span>著作信息</span></h2>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>标题：</strong>SCP-1925-JP - 圣女堕胎<br />
<strong>原文：</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-1925-jp">http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-1925-jp</a><br />
<strong>作者：</strong>©︎<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinoemon" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4356892); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4356892&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609664625" alt="Kinoemon" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4356892)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinoemon" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4356892); return false;">Kinoemon</a></span><br />
<strong>创作年份：</strong> 2019<br />
<strong>翻译：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/katja1453" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6985866); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6985866&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609664625" alt="Katja1453" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6985866)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/katja1453" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6985866); return false;">Katja1453</a></span></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scp-jp.wikidot.com/local--files/scp-1925-jp/pregnant-1245703_1280.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="pregnant-1245703_1280.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>SCP-1925-JP-1的照片。此时项目处于中期后11小时</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>项目编号:</strong> SCP-1925-JP</p>
<p><strong>项目等级:</strong> Euclid</p>
<p><strong>特殊收容措施:</strong>。SCP-1925-JP-1和SCP-1925-JP-2应被收容于Site-8128内的人形实体收容室。医疗小组应监视SCP-1925-JP-1的身体状况，给予相应的治疗并缓解其痛苦。对SCP-1925-JP-2消失后的去向之调查应持续进行。</p>
<p><strong>描述:</strong> SCP-1925-JP为围绕<span class="ruby">能取 真理<span class="rt">Notori Mari</span></span>(以下称SCP-1925-JP-1）以及人形实体(以下称SCP-1925-JP-2）发生的一系列现象的统称。SCP-1925-JP如下文所述分为4个活动期与1个中间期，并以约6天为周期重复发生。<br />
<br /></p>
